1. To start with the NodeJs we need to install nodejs 

            https://nodejs.org/en/download

            install latest version with (LTS) only

    To check weather nodejs installed or not open terminal with 
        ->  windows + R  
            ->  type  'cmd
                ->  now type  'npm -v'
                    11.0.0

                ->  Start with Demo code in terminal
                
                    C:\Users\smani>node
